Vanderpump Rules is an American reality television series on Bravo, featuring "The Real Housewives of Beverly Hills" cast member Lisa Vanderpump in the title role and her staff at Vanderpump's West Hollywood, California restaurant SUR. The series premiered on January 7, 2013.
Andy Cohen stated during the "Watch What Happens Live" episode on February 4, 2013 that there will be a Vanderpump Rules reunion. The reunion was filmed on February 9, 2013.
Premise.
The series follows Lisa Vanderpump as she divides her time between her motherly duties and hectic business. It also encompasses the employees at SUR as they work on building their futures.
VanderDolls Rules.
VanderDolls Rules is an eight part online series created by Bravo that tells the love story between Stassi and Jax using dolls. It contains actual audio from the series. 
